common

Interface IGetAlgoCommandMessage


  • public interface IGetAlgoCommandMessage
    Message type that should be sent to a user to request an algoCommand corresponding to the class returned by requestedClass. Considered a "well known type"; it is required that you have a command for this type! As this is a "well known type", the command for this type should be written as an anonymous inner class to your model so that it can directly reference your model's algorithm.
